40000.English_Text: Let's see here. What came in today?

40001.English_Text: Coming all the way here to the Peach Blossom was worthwhile.
40001.Chinese_Text: 不枉我不远千里来到桃花商廛。

40002.Chinese_Text: 呜呜…我是不是没有才能…

40003.English_Text: ...I got scolded by my master again.

40004.English_Text: This is the famous Soul Bridge!

40005.English_Text: I heard there are many Barons at Soul Bridge.
40005.Chinese_Text: 听说灵交院里有很多巴隆～

40006.English_Text: There is a legend behind this lighthouse...
40006.Chinese_Text: 有一个关于这个灯塔的传说…

40007.Original_Text: 난… 전설 같은 건 믿지 않아...

40009.Original_Text: 나도 언젠간 이런 큰 배를 가질거야!
40009.English_Text: I'm going to own a ship like this someday!
40009.Chinese_Text: 我总有一天也要拥有这么大的一艘船！

40011.Original_Text: 저 먼 바다 끝엔 뭐가 있을까?
40011.English_Text: I wonder what lies on the other side of the ocean.
40011.Chinese_Text: 海洋的尽头会有什么呢？

40012.English_Text: Maybe I could see it if I was atop the clouds?
40012.Chinese_Text: 飞到云端上面能看见吗？

40014.Original_Text: 이번에 새로 만든 낫이 아주 잘 들어.
40014.English_Text: This new scythe works very well.
40014.Chinese_Text: 这次新做的镰刀很锐利。

40015.English_Text: I heard that the Soul Steel can enhance weapons.
40015.Chinese_Text: 听说金庚哲门还会帮忙强化武器。

40016.English_Text: The Soul Steel are known for their excellent skills.
40016.Chinese_Text: 金庚哲门的手艺可是出了名的好哦？

40017.Original_Text: 하지만 우리같은 사람들이 그럴 일이나 있겠어?
40017.English_Text: But, what's the use for ordinary people like us?
40017.Chinese_Text: 但是我们这种人会遇到那种事吗？

40021.English_Text: It's so much fun at the festival!
40021.Chinese_Text: 难得一见的庆典真令人开心！

40022.English_Text: Make a bet and earn some money!

40023.Original_Text: 현재 최대 배당금 4배! 인생 역전의 기회가 왔어요~!
40023.English_Text: Get 4-fold your bet! A life-changing chance!
40023.Chinese_Text: 目前最高赔率为4倍！一夜暴富的机会来了～！

40025.Original_Text: 이번에 한 몫 크게 챙겨서 떠야지…
40025.English_Text: I'm going to hit the jackpot and leave!
40025.Chinese_Text: 这次一定要大赚一笔后离开…

40032.Original_Text: 에휴.. 대체 무슨 일이 일어나는 건지…
40032.English_Text: What the heck is going on...?

40033.Chinese_Text: 不知道孩子们有没有事…

40039.English_Text:
That warrior at the
finals was amazing...
40039.Chinese_Text:
决赛的那个人…
真的很厉害…

40040.English_Text:
I wish I could meet
the warrior again.
40040.Chinese_Text:
啊啊…在哪里
可以再见一面呢？

40041.Original_Text: 자네들 내 말 듣고 있나?\n내 똑똑히 봤다니까!
40041.English_Text:
Are you listening to me?
I saw it with my own eyes!
40041.Chinese_Text:
你们没有在听我说话吗？
我亲眼看到了！

40042.English_Text:
The entire Sapphire Basin
could have disappeared!
40042.Chinese_Text:
整个半月湖差点就
完全消失了！

40043.English_Text:
Hey, you!
Are you coming from the Fish Network?
40043.Chinese_Text:
喂，你！
你是从大鱼坊过来的吗？

40044.English_Text:
Is it true?
Has a Fissure been found?
40044.Chinese_Text:
那是真的吗？
就是裂缝出现的消息！

30001000001.English_Text:
Looking for members to accompany
the venerable Jimmy Ace!
30001000001.Chinese_Text:
招募与伟大的吉米神一起
狩猎的团员！

30001000002.English_Text:
High salary guaranteed!
Plus a job for life!
30001000002.Chinese_Text:
保证高额报酬！
保证一生铁饭碗！

30001000003.Original_Text: 자자~ 날이면 날마다 오는\n단원 모집이 아니란 말이야~
30001000003.English_Text:
Now, now! Opportunities like this
don't come by very often.
30001000003.Chinese_Text:
来来～招募团员可不是
天天都有的机会哦～

30001000004.English_Text:
Looking for members to accompany
the venerable Jimmy Ace!
30001000004.Chinese_Text:
招募与伟大的吉米神一起
狩猎的团员！

30001000005.Original_Text: 고액 보수 보장!\n가족 같은 복지 보장!
30001000005.English_Text:
High salary guaranteed!
Plus great benefits!
30001000005.Chinese_Text:
保证高额报酬！
像家人一样的福利！

30001000006.Original_Text: 자자~ 날이면 날마다 오는\n단원 모집이 아니야~
30001000006.English_Text:
Now now! opportunities like this
don't come by very often.
30001000006.Chinese_Text:
来来～招募团员可不是
天天都有的机会哦～

30001000007.English_Text:
Looking for members to accompany
the venerable Jimmy Ace!
30001000007.Chinese_Text:
招募与伟大的吉米神一起
狩猎的团员！

30001000008.Original_Text: 고액 보수 보장!\n반달호수에 휘날릴 명성 보장!
30001000008.English_Text:
High salary guaranteed!
Plus fame throughout Sapphire Basin!
30001000008.Chinese_Text:
保证高额报酬！
保证名扬半月湖！

30001000009.Original_Text: 자자~ 날이면 날마다 오는\n단원 모집이 아니야~
30001000009.English_Text:
Now now! opportunities like this
don't come by very often.
30001000009.Chinese_Text:
来来～招募团员可不是
天天都有的机会哦～

30001000010.English_Text:
Looking for members to accompany
the venerable Jimmy Ace!
30001000010.Chinese_Text:
招募与伟大的吉米神一起
狩猎的团员！

30001000011.English_Text:
Hazard pay guaranteed!
Plus a lifetime contract!
30001000011.Chinese_Text:
保证生命保险！
保证一生铁饭碗！

30001000012.Original_Text: 자자~ 날이면 날마다 오는\n단원 모집이 아니란 말이야~
30001000012.English_Text:
Now, now! Opportunities like this
don't come by very often.
30001000012.Chinese_Text:
来来～招募团员可不是
天天都有的机会哦～

30001000013.English_Text:
Looking for members to accompany
the venerable Jimmy Ace!
30001000013.Chinese_Text:
招募与伟大的吉米神一起
狩猎的团员！

30001000014.English_Text:
High salary guaranteed!
Work-life balance guaranteed!
30001000014.Chinese_Text:
保证高额报酬！
保证自由时间！

30001000015.Original_Text: 자자~ 날이면 날마다 오는\n단원 모집이 아니란 말이야~
30001000015.English_Text:
Now, now! Opportunities like this
don't come by very often.
30001000015.Chinese_Text:
来来～招募团员可不是
天天都有的机会哦～

30001000020.Original_Text: 대장~ 추수갓 대장니임~!\n대체 어딜 가신 거야?
30001000020.English_Text:
Mr. Jimmy Ace!
Where the heck is he?
30001000020.Chinese_Text:
队长～吉米神队长～！
到底在哪里？

30001000021.Original_Text: 어휴, 그냥 얼른 도망가자!\n여긴 너무 위험해!
30001000021.English_Text:
I should run!
It's too dangerous here!
30001000021.Chinese_Text:
唉，还是快点逃走吧！
这里很危险！

30001000023.Original_Text: 아, 언제까지 찾으러 다닐 거야?\n난 위험한건 딱 질색이라고.
30001000023.English_Text:
When does this search end?
This seems too dangerous!
30001000023.Chinese_Text:
唉，你想找到什么时候？
我最讨厌危险的事情。

30001000025.English_Text:
There is the ocean...
I want to go back...
30001000025.Chinese_Text:
看到了大海...
我想回去，呜呜。

30001000028.English_Text:
Come on!
There's been a misunderstanding!
30001000028.Chinese_Text:
所以说～
这是误会，误会～

30001000030.Original_Text: 자자~ 날이면 날마다 오는\n단원 모집이 아니란 말이야~
30001000030.English_Text:
Now, now! Opportunities like this
don't come by very often.
30001000030.Chinese_Text:
来来～招募团员可不是
天天都有的机会哦～

30001000031.Original_Text: 위대하신 추수갓님과 함께 할\n신입 단원 모집!
30001000031.English_Text:
Looking for new recruits to accompany
the venerable Jimmy Ace!
30001000031.Chinese_Text:
招募与伟大的吉米神一起
狩猎的新手团员！

30001000032.English_Text:
Great salary...
Anyone up for Hesuth hunting?
30001000032.Chinese_Text:
保证...高额报酬...
有人想狩猎海兽吗...

30001000033.Original_Text: 난 이제 어쩌나… \n대장도 없고, 우두둑도 없고…
30001000033.English_Text:
What to do...
without both the boss and Munchi?
30001000033.Chinese_Text:
我该怎么办...
队长也不在，钗石也不在...

30001000034.Original_Text: 크하하하하! 아무렴 어때?\n와도 그만, 안 와도 그만이야.
30001000034.English_Text:
Hahaha! No worries!
We've got nothing to lose.
30001000034.Chinese_Text:
哇哈哈哈哈！那有什么关系？
来也好，不来也罢。

30001000037.Original_Text: 자자~ 날이면 날마다 오는\n단원 모집이 아니란 말이야~
30001000037.English_Text:
Now, now! Opportunities like this
don't come by very often.
30001000037.Chinese_Text:
来来～招募团员可不是
天天都有的机会哦～

30001000038.English_Text:
Looking for members to accompany
the venerable Jimmy Ace!
30001000038.Chinese_Text:
招募与伟大的吉米神一起
狩猎的团员！

30001000039.English_Text: Khahahaha~ After all, this body is the best!
30001000039.Chinese_Text: 哈哈哈哈~毕竟这个身体最好！

30001000040.Original_Text: 아무렴요! 해수 사냥꾼 하면 추수갓! \n추수갓 하면 해수 사냥꾼인걸요!
30001000040.English_Text: Anyway! If you say seawater hunter, you are Harvest God! \nIf you say Harvest God, you are a seawater hunter!
30001000040.Chinese_Text: 反正！你说海水猎手，你就是丰收神！\n如果你说丰收神，你就是海水猎手！

30001000043.English_Text: You just need to listen to me.

30001000047.English_Text: It's okay, I'll definitely come alone.
30001000047.Chinese_Text: 没关系，我一定一个人来。

30001000049.English_Text: Captain, what shall we do now?

30001000052.English_Text: I can't see a single rat!
